{"tid":837629,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"范冰冰「國際知名」亦可被失蹤 CNN：沒有人是安全的","createTime":"2018-09-26T13:45:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T15:03:40.000Z","uid":150685,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9631588910a4da6822903224d5813d1f7afdaecc","tid":837629,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T13:45:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180926/large/1537935191_09f4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180926%2Flarge%2F1537935191_09f4.jpg&h=650ad7d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大陸女星范冰冰捲入「逃稅風暴」，至今已經「神隱」超過三個月，各種傳聞湧現，有講過佢被軟禁喺酒店，亦有傳佢秘密去咗美國，但范冰冰一直未見公開現身，只係試過喺今個月16日生日當天，喺微博上線，刪除咗一條系統自動發佈嘅「生日快樂」post。<br />\n<br />\n今日美國傳媒《CNN》刊登一篇署名文章，標題為：Fan Bingbing's disappearance shows no one is safe from Beijing，撰文嘅Michael Caster於twitter稱自己係維權人士、研究員，過往亦曾多次發表中國人權問題嘅文章。<br />\n<br />\n文中提到，如果連范冰冰呢個級數嘅「國際知名藝人」都可以喺中國突然被消失，文中直指「no one is safe from Beijing」，喺中國根本就冇任何人身安全，報道仲提到有唔少維權人士及記者都被失蹤過，而自范冰冰消失以嚟，中國官方從未向外宣佈過任務消息，根據中國的「指定居所監視居住」（RSDL）政策，警方可秘密拘留一個人超過六個月，文中質疑喺中國被失蹤嘅事已經越嚟越嚴重，提醒於中國境內嘅任何人都有可能成為受害者。<br />\n<br />\n《CNN》曾經喺17年向中國外交部提問有關中國司法及人權嘅問題，當時中國外交部嘅回應表示「中國是一個法治國家」（A Country with a rule of law），仲話「中國司法保證了犯人所有法律權益」，更強烈呼籲外國媒體要尊重中國司法權、鄭重事實咁去報道。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180926/58724338\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180926%2F58724338&d=6AyKI7P%2BGQ6coZ8Cu2pPOZzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=0da63887\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180926%2F58724338&h=e56e2e4c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180926/58724338</a>"},{"pid":"b2eaa3e6c0e09dbb042cfd9ea96696ad8e27f4db","tid":837629,"uid":156618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T13:51:47.000Z","msg":"點止被失蹤，被自殺都有啦<br />\n<br />\n所以冇事冇幹真係唔好去地獄鬼國"},{"pid":"4e632feabdec8276209994010d7e0de24f0ce6ca","tid":837629,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T13:53:47.000Z","msg":"其實范冰冰就算出返黎可以講d乜<br />\n<br />\n不如當佢死左算啦"},{"pid":"a51acf90102281f8eed3aec10c5b58be48ee0873","tid":837629,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2eaa3e6c0e09dbb042cfd9ea96696ad8e27f4db","tid":837629,"uid":156618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T13:51:47.000Z","msg":"點止被失蹤，被自殺都有啦<br />\n<br />\n所以冇事冇幹真係唔好去地獄鬼國"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T13:53:53.000Z","msg":"中國香港呢"},{"pid":"d7e097f2e1e280702c47bb03ae70ea9c9190af26","tid":837629,"uid":54060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a51acf90102281f8eed3aec10c5b58be48ee0873","tid":837629,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2eaa3e6c0e09dbb042cfd9ea96696ad8e27f4db","tid":837629,"uid":156618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T13:51:47.000Z","msg":"點止被失蹤，被自殺都有啦<br />\n<br />\n所以冇事冇幹真係唔好去地獄鬼國"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T13:53:53.000Z","msg":"中國香港呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T14:54:18.000Z","msg":"家下洗頭艇都唔撚使<br />\n一野車鳩你去西九就搞撚掂<br />\n個度已經割撚咗俾支那<br />\n警犬都無權搜查"},{"pid":"22fbea8e8188551c3e82eed5bbec6a62cab38ea8","tid":837629,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7e097f2e1e280702c47bb03ae70ea9c9190af26","tid":837629,"uid":54060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a51acf90102281f8eed3aec10c5b58be48ee0873","tid":837629,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2eaa3e6c0e09dbb042cfd9ea96696ad8e27f4db","tid":837629,"uid":156618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T13:51:47.000Z","msg":"點止被失蹤，被自殺都有啦<br />\n<br />\n所以冇事冇幹真係唔好去地獄鬼國"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T13:53:53.000Z","msg":"中國香港呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T14:54:18.000Z","msg":"家下洗頭艇都